    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1849_138063_000003_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1849/138063/1849_138063_000003_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1849",
        "content": "In the middle of the court was a catafalque, raised about two yards above the ground and covered completely by an immense canopy of black velvet, and on the steps all round it white wax tapers burned in more than a hundred silver candlesticks.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1849_138063_000003_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1849/138063/1849_138063_000003_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1849",
        "content": "Upon the catafalque was seen the dead body of a damsel so lovely that by her beauty she made death itself look beautiful.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1849_138063_000003_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1849/138063/1849_138063_000003_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1849",
        "content": "She lay with her head resting upon a cushion of brocade and crowned with a garland of sweet smelling flowers of divers sorts, her hands crossed upon her bosom, and between them a branch of yellow palm of victory.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1849_138063_000003_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1849/138063/1849_138063_000003_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1849",
        "content": "Nor was this all, for Don Quixote had perceived that the dead body on the catafalque was that of the fair Altisidora.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1849_138063_000003_000009",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1849/138063/1849_138063_000003_000009.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1849",
        "content": "As the duke and duchess mounted the stage Don Quixote and Sancho rose and made them a profound obeisance, which they returned by bowing their heads slightly.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1849_138063_000003_000010",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1849/138063/1849_138063_000003_000010.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1849",
        "content": "At this moment an official crossed over, and approaching Sancho threw over him a robe of black buckram painted all over with flames of fire, and taking off his cap put upon his head a mitre such as those undergoing the sentence of the Holy Office wear; and whispered in his ear that he must not open his lips, or they would put a gag upon him, or take his life.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1849_138063_000003_000011",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1849/138063/1849_138063_000003_000011.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1849",
        "content": "Sancho surveyed himself from head to foot and saw himself all ablaze with flames; but as they did not burn him, he did not care two farthings for them.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1849_138063_000006_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1849/138063/1849_138063_000006_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1849",
        "content": "At this point one of the two that looked like kings exclaimed, \"Enough, enough, divine singer!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1849_138063_000007_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1849/138063/1849_138063_000007_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1849",
        "content": "No sooner had Minos the fellow judge of Rhadamanthus said this, than Rhadamanthus rising up said:",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1849_138063_000009_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1849/138063/1849_138063_000009_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1849",
        "content": "On hearing this Sancho broke silence and cried out, \"By all that's good, I'll as soon let my face be smacked or handled as turn Moor.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1849_138063_000009_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1849/138063/1849_138063_000009_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1849",
        "content": "Try those jokes on a brother in law; 'I'm an old dog, and \"tus, tus\" is no use with me.'\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1849_138063_000010_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1849/138063/1849_138063_000010_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1849",
        "content": "\"Thou shalt die,\" said Rhadamanthus in a loud voice; \"relent, thou tiger; humble thyself, proud Nimrod; suffer and be silent, for no impossibilities are asked of thee; it is not for thee to inquire into the difficulties in this matter; smacked thou must be, pricked thou shalt see thyself, and with pinches thou must be made to howl.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1849_138063_000010_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1849/138063/1849_138063_000010_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1849",
        "content": "Ho, I say, officials, obey my orders; or by the word of an honest man, ye shall see what ye were born for.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1849_138063_000012_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1849/138063/1849_138063_000012_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1849",
        "content": "Here Don Quixote, too, broke silence, saying to Sancho, \"Have patience, my son, and gratify these noble persons, and give all thanks to heaven that it has infused such virtue into thy person, that by its sufferings thou canst disenchant the enchanted and restore to life the dead.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1849_138063_000014_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1849/138063/1849_138063_000014_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1849",
        "content": "\"Less politeness and less paint, senora duenna,\" said Sancho; \"by God your hands smell of vinegar wash.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1849_138063_000017_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1849/138063/1849_138063_000017_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1849",
        "content": "Rhadamanthus bade Sancho put away his wrath, as the object they had in view was now attained.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1849_138063_000018_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1849/138063/1849_138063_000018_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1849",
        "content": "To which Sancho made answer, \"That's trick upon trick, I think, and not honey upon pancakes; a nice thing it would be for a whipping to come now, on the top of pinches, smacks, and pin proddings!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1849_138063_000018_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1849/138063/1849_138063_000018_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1849",
        "content": "Leave me alone; or else by God I'll fling the whole thing to the dogs, let come what may.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1849_138063_000028_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1849/138063/1849_138063_000028_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1849",
        "content": "Thereupon the duke seized the opportunity of practising this mystification upon him; so much did he enjoy everything connected with Sancho and Don Quixote.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1849_138063_000030_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1849/138063/1849_138063_000030_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1849",
        "content": "O harder thou than marble to my plaint;",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1849_138063_000032_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1849/138063/1849_138063_000032_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1849",
        "content": "For of course that's where one who dies in despair is bound for.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1849_138063_000035_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1849/138063/1849_138063_000035_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1849",
        "content": "If it should be good, faithful, and true, it will have ages of life; but if it should be bad, from its birth to its burial will not be a very long journey.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
